Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----OPlrcJPN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.75,0:01:16.38,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}憧れを書きとめて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:19.13,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}いつか叶える日のために
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.22,0:01:24.60,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}折り目つけたあのページを　開きたい時がきた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:29.94,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}巻き起こるアレコレで　見失うこともあるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:32.69,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}ねっ、大丈夫　踏み出してる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:35.32,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}はじまりは想定外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.48,0:01:38.11,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}君が消せないまま残した
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:40.86,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}寂しがりだった記憶さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.91,0:01:44.95,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}読み替えてみせるよ　明るい方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.99,0:01:50.37,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}たったそれだけで全てが変わる気がするから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:51.67,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}All Right
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:54.71,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}だから　さあおいで　そのままで！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.75,0:01:57.55,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}弱虫も隠さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.67,0:01:58.76,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}"On my Sheep"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:02.43,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}夢乗せ　待ち合わせよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.59,0:02:08.31,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}この冒険記を綴る中　君の名を呼んでも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:14.82,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}もう迷子じゃない　一緒の旅を始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:22.16,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}そう…きみと、わたし、もっと！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----OPlrcCHN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.75,0:01:16.38,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}記下你的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:19.13,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}以迎接它變成現實的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.22,0:01:24.60,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}折疊起來的書頁  正在呼喚著我去翻閱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:29.94,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}揚起的風沙塵土  可能會讓你迷失方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:32.69,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}但是不要擔心  我們在堅定前行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:35.32,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}只是開端有點意想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.48,0:01:38.11,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}你記錄下的寂寞經歷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:40.86,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}無法擦去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.91,0:01:44.95,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}但我會解讀成未來的財富
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.99,0:01:50.37,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}如此小的努力就能讓我感到世界煥然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:51.67,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}All Right
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:54.71,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}所以  跟我來吧  就這樣出發！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.75,0:01:57.55,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}沒有什麼好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.67,0:01:58.76,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}"On my Sheep"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:02.43,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}放飛夢想  相約明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.59,0:02:08.31,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}書寫這篇歷險記的時候  即使呼喚你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:14.82,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}那也不意味著迷路  而是共同啟程的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:22.16,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}沒錯…你與我 不會停步！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----EDlrcJPN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:53.73,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}始まりのベル　鍵をかける音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.28,0:22:01.53,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}流れゆく間に大人になる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:07.27,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}走り　はしゃぎ　過ごす日々が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:11.51,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}遠ざかるときがくる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:16.01,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ここで出した答えを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.01,0:22:28.20,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ああ　どこかで語り継げたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.01,0:22:33.48,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}迷いながら歩く人波を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.74,0:22:37.81,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}照らし出す光になれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.92,0:22:46.02,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}包まれてたグリーンベルトの先
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.23,0:22:54.36,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}続く明日を目指してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----EDlrcCHN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:53.73,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}起始之鈴  上鎖之聲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.28,0:22:01.53,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}在它們的流淌中  我們逐漸成長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:07.27,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}奔跑歡笑的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:11.51,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}終歸會遠去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:16.01,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}此刻得出的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.01,0:22:28.20,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只要將它流傳下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.01,0:22:33.48,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}即使是迷惘而行的人潮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.74,0:22:37.81,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}也能將其引領
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.92,0:22:46.02,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}沿著綠蔭大道走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.23,0:22:54.36,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}就能到達期望的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----TXT-----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千莉  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.72,0:00:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.19,0:00:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千莉…你什麼都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.94,0:02:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧同學還沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.44,0:02:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能鼓起勇氣拜託他  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.29,0:02:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我可不能讓他失望  要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  筧同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.22,0:03:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我這就開門
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.61,0:03:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  我剛到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個房間是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能輕易把這份安穩交出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  儀左大人有飼主嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠幾歲了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.85,0:03:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.61,0:03:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠三餐是怎麼解決的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧同學你真是喜歡書
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.53,0:03:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為讀書長知識
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愛學知識呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:03:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書是驅散黑暗的光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得越多世界就越光明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能越發接近安穩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能嘗出是什麼味道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檸檬…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草莓？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總算是肯把臉朝向我這邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.64,0:04:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧同學  你會陪我一直到黃金週吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要加油  讓你黃金週過後也想和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  筧同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我們一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撿垃圾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.29,0:04:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撿垃圾這種事  認真做起來的話說不定還挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能算是學校的萬事屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:05:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想建立一個解決大家困難和煩惱的組織
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果一上來就讓別人找我們商量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不會有人信賴我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要提高知名度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時也要積累活動成果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撿垃圾太不起眼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是不行的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎你是領隊  就按你的想法做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey  筧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接我這一球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接得好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們夠了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太沒教養了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大膽子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.94,0:05:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧  高峰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:05:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是汐美HAPPY  PROJECT
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要和我們一起撿垃圾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會借給您手套和夾子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束時間是可以自由安排的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撿垃圾還是流行不起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  堅持下去的話  遲早會有人答應的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像搭訕呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧同學  你搭訕過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從沒做過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.77,0:06:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜  是你的話一定能成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎你會答應嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逗你玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.41,0:06:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別臉紅呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是汐美HAPPY  PROJECT
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  您是筧…學長？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是日光浴食堂的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:06:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是鈴木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真高興你記得我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過我的名字了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上網頁新聞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然乍一看是色狼行為
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.29,0:07:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但實際是從事故中救下女生的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs16}【重要】對脫軌事故報導的致歉與訂正
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs13}在此前發生的路面電車脫軌事故新聞報導中，有部份內容有誤，在此深表歉意。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs13}該報導中以「脫軌事故發生時所拍照片」為題刊登了男生把手搭在女生胸部上的照片。\N由於乍看之下是色狼行為，本社進行了詳細採訪。\N事件真相是，由於女生處在電車行進軌跡上，男生發現這一情況而進行了救助。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望月學姐她說到做到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果是我欠下她人情了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們做的事挺有趣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有興趣  請一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  OK
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.42,0:07:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以？不是被硬拉進來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡這樣湊熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小女子鈴木佳奈  會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:08:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人行嗎  我幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.90,0:08:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝您的好意  不過會弄髒衣服的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不用您費心的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.94,0:08:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,500日元呀  怪不得費勁也要取
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  畢竟金額不小
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  讓您衣服髒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正一直在撿垃圾  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.86,0:08:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣  我也要感謝你招待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭了  學長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  出力了  出大力了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撿了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  第一次活動的紀念
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天說的調查牧羊人的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微收集了下網上的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一晚上搜集了這麼多？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是複製貼上的資料而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事誰都會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  小玉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一半多是類似都市傳說的傳言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對形象的描述也各不相同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有來信指示  有見面交談
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照說的去做  就實現了願望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大致就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有用郵件的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  我試著回覆過那條郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但到現在還沒回覆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回覆了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是騷擾郵件怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正不會死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上  我昨天收到了牧羊人的郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是命運的邂逅什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.23,0:10:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佳  這是命運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說大家都收到牧羊人的郵件了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看看你收到的郵件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  是發送到電腦的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在沒手機
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒手機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…弄壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}小佳你頭髮真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.02,0:10:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}哪裡哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  肚子餓了  去吃點東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.47,0:10:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}用的是什麼洗髮精？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音叉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.97,0:11:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是音樂科的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.39,0:11:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  上面有字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（第三十屆青少年聲樂大賽  冠軍）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是私人物品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.48,0:11:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就得到第5個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第6個人的契機也搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.86,0:11:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  你們要不斷增進感情喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.01,0:11:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芹澤水結的After  School  Avenue
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.20,0:11:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位覺得如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們以御園千莉同學的天使般的歌聲結束
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:12:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉  現在已經不再播報失物認領了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣的委託會沒完沒了的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…是在哪裡撿到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在中央大道上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.85,0:12:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我看一看嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你認識失主嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說認不認識…這可是御園千莉的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御園？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那位歌姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是超有名的人嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.27,0:12:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧同學你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉呢  這傢伙只知道看書  不諳世故
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.09,0:12:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是音樂科備受期待的新生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在今年的入學典禮上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也作為壓軸上台唱歌了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  那真是棒極了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全就是天使的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  她還留著這東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺有些隱情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過今天已經很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再去找御園吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.61,0:13:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴木同學  讓你陪我們真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.07,0:13:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我還能跟你們一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.62,0:13:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在活動室等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在大圖書館
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.21,0:13:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那麼明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是要去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御園同學的家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交給筧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙可是很少會主動行動的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  還麻煩你陪我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:13:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人去我畢竟不太放心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:14:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  原來你不信任我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是非得今天去找御園同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概這東西是有著某種意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今遺失了  她說不定正在傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓她傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.85,0:14:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你們素不相識啊  也要這樣做？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.04,0:14:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  白崎  為什麼你要努力到這種地步？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過想要改變自己的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會有那種想法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.59,0:14:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御園同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.17,0:14:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自動販賣機那裡的…學長？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:15:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們在中央大道上撿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.01,0:15:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是你的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處都找不著  還以為再也找不回來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你是在找它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天的自動販賣機那裡也已經找過了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻沒有找到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.96,0:15:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很重要的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是回憶的信物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常重要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又幫了我一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.15,0:15:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼漂亮的音叉  我還是第一次見到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.44,0:15:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是歌姬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.63,0:15:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道  因為我是歌姬才為我送過來的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  因為你讓我看了好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好東西是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.09,0:15:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說正經的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正在做一些類似於志工的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  白崎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐美HAPPY  PROJECT？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到什麼煩惱的話  隨時可以跟我們聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想…再經歷那種事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是下次吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.48,0:16:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴木同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚…晚上好！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才回家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.32,0:16:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  你要買手機嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧學長  方便的話能陪我一起看看嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}欲知後事請繼續觀賞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:16:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}這啥玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:16:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}哇  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很難操作的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很可愛的嘛  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小兔兔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單才是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  是智慧型手機呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺就是不太一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.02,0:17:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  跟您配個情侶機可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.84,0:17:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  筧學長  你這樣很傷人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是每天都要使用的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買自己喜歡的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  筧同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.76,0:17:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  我剛到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御園同學的HAPPY  PROJECT能順利進展
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:17:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:18:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個看起來很重要  想快一點還給她而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也要努力才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.32,0:18:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓學校變得更加更加快樂！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  她跟我這種人不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.51,0:18:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是想…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是這裡的鑰匙  交給白崎你保管了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都決定要幫你了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.51,0:18:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好保管的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.49,0:18:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是部室的鑰匙而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以扣上鑰匙圈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給大家配副鑰匙也行  可不要弄丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才不會弄丟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.25,0:18:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芹澤水結的After  School  Avenue
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.96,0:18:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在接下來三十分鐘左右的時間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請各位跟我一起散步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟昨天的聲音完全不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專業的就是不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏘鏘  手機！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好可愛！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.98,0:19:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SM04D嗎  這款我也很喜歡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.35,0:19:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來交換郵箱吧  郵箱！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好狡猾啊  高峰同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想知道小佳的郵箱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個冷靜一點  鈴木同學都被你們嚇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝各位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.33,0:19:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.47,0:19:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用說那麼多遍  我能聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就給我反省一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從門外面都能聽到你們嘰嘰喳喳的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人數增加了一個！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是新加入的部員鈴木佳奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佳  你要加入嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了不要吵了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦  觀賞下小貓來冷靜下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.65,0:20:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,COME  ON  HOLD  ME  TIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把…把牠拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你討厭貓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動物…我受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.89,0:20:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.47,0:20:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總…總之
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們給我安靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以嗎  鈴木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我鈴木就行  昨天久違地痛快了一回
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想跟各位繼續相處下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.84,0:20:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御園千莉會讓你們了解非常重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧羊人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:21:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的郵箱有告訴別人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.93,0:21:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒告訴任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不同尋常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這明顯是掌握了我們的行動才發郵件給我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想讓我們跟御園同學接觸嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅長電腦的人應該能查到是誰發的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看那人的水平的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.33,0:21:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.45,0:21:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是學生食堂引以為傲的人才
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.31,0:21:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹽麹炸雞胸肉和凱撒沙拉和義式三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.82,0:21:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合計一千日元
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加一份你的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.05,0:21:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  追加合計一萬日元
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.14,0:23:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選這個嗎  但是這個也不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.82,0:23:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心情很好呢白崎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玉  筧同學把圖書部的鑰匙給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.77,0:23:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.77,0:23:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選哪個鑰匙圈好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.86,0:23:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧  你居然想用鑰匙來提升白崎的好感？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去我的白崎就…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.64,0:23:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玉你喜歡哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.56,0:23:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我當然是喜歡白崎你…啊嚏
